Title: r.gwflow
Abstract: Numerical calculation program for transient, confined and unconfined groundwater flow in two dimensions.

Input.Title: phead
Input.Abstract: The initial piezometric head in [m]

Input.Title: status
Input.Abstract: Boundary condition status, 0-inactive, 1-active, 2-dirichlet

Input.Title: hc_x
Input.Abstract: X-part of the hydraulic conductivity tensor in [m/s]

Input.Title: hc_y
Input.Abstract: Y-part of the hydraulic conductivity tensor in [m/s]

Input.Title: q
Input.Abstract: Water sources and sinks in [m^3/s]

Input.Title: s
Input.Abstract: Specific yield in [1/m]

Input.Title: recharge
Input.Abstract: Recharge map e.g: 6*10^-9 per cell in [m^3/s*m^2]

Input.Title: top
Input.Abstract: Top surface of the aquifer in [m]

Input.Title: bottom
Input.Abstract: Bottom surface of the aquifer in [m]

Input.Title: type
Input.Abstract: The type of groundwater flow

Input.Title: river_bed
Input.Abstract: The height of the river bed in [m]

Input.Title: river_head
Input.Abstract: Water level (head) of the river with leakage connection in [m]

Input.Title: river_leak
Input.Abstract: The leakage coefficient of the river bed in [1/s]

Input.Title: drain_bed
Input.Abstract: The height of the drainage bed in [m]

Input.Title: drain_leak
Input.Abstract: The leakage coefficient of the drainage bed in [1/s]

Input.Title: dtime
Input.Abstract: The calculation time in seconds

Input.Title: maxit
Input.Abstract: Maximum number of iteration used to solver the linear equation system

Input.Title: error
Input.Abstract: Error break criteria for iterative solvers (jacobi, sor, cg or bicgstab)

Input.Title: solver
Input.Abstract: The type of solver which should solve the symmetric linear equation system

Input.Title: relax
Input.Abstract: The relaxation parameter used by the jacobi and sor solver for speedup or stabilizing

Input.Title: -f
Input.Abstract: Allocate a full quadratic linear equation system, default is a sparse linear equation system

Input.Title: output
Input.Abstract: Groundwater flow

Input.Title: vx
Input.Abstract: Groundwater filter velocity vector part in x direction [m/s]

Input.Title: vy
Input.Abstract: Groundwater filter velocity vector part in y direction [m/s]

Input.Title: budget
Input.Abstract: Groundwater budget for each cell [m^3/s]

Input.Title: GRASS_REGION_PARAMETER
Input.Abstract: GRASS GIS 7 region extent

Input.Title: GRASS_REGION_CELLSIZE_PARAMETER
Input.Abstract: GRASS GIS 7 region cellsize (leave 0 for default)

Input.Title: GRASS_RASTER_FORMAT_OPT
Input.Abstract: Output Rasters format options (createopt)

Input.Title: GRASS_RASTER_FORMAT_META
Input.Abstract: Output Rasters format metadata options (metaopt)

Output.Title: vx
Output.Abstract: Groundwater filter velocity vector part in x direction [m/s]

Output.Title: vy
Output.Abstract: Groundwater filter velocity vector part in y direction [m/s]
